name: Una portada para un disco de Camilo Sesto
description:
This image is part of a series called "Manos" (Hands), created for a daily photography challenge. It was my first conceptual photography project. 

"Una portada para un disco de Camilo Sesto" (An album cover for Camilo Sesto), refers to a famous Spanish singer-songwriter, especially popular in the seventies and eighties, mainly known for his romantic ballads.

For more content, find me on Social Media as @lauridomm
